This is a very simple dajngo blog app.
Only appropriate for linux OS
Django version: 1.10.4 
OS: Centos 7.0
Python: 2.7 
How to test with this app
Clone the codes to your linux:
# git clone git@github.com:lufy90/Blog
Edit the setting.py about the host address, change the address to you address:
# vim blog/setting.py
ALLOWED_HOSTS = [u'192.168.10.10']
Then you can run the server with in Blog directory:
[user@host Blog]# ./manager runserver 0.0.0.0:8000

If you have the right firewall and network configuration, now the site can be 
visit from browser:
http://192.168.10.10:8000

This app can also deploy with nginx, need make some configuration about nginx.
